app_details.title: M-PESA Safaricom Ethiopia
app_details.description:
Introducing the new M-PESA Safaricom Ethiopia App! Enjoy safe, easy, and convenient financial and communication services all in one app. Send money, pay merchants and bills, buy airtime, buy bundles and packages, check airtime usage, and withdraw money with just a few taps on your mobile phone. With the new and simplified user experience, you can manage your finances effortlessly. Plus, you can use the app in offline mode, track your spends, and authenticate transactions with biometrics. Simplify your life and download the M-PESA Safaricom Ethiopia App today.
 

• Core M-PESA transactions - Access all core M-PESA transactions with a simplified experience - Send money, pay merchants and bills with M-PESA, withdraw at agent or ATM and buy airtime.

• Core Safaricom transactions -  Manage your Safaricom account with ease. Check your airtime, voice and internet balances, check your consumption, top up, buy bundles, get PUK, and much more.

• Offline Mode - Log in and transact on the app (Send Money, pay with M-PESA, withdraw and buy airtime) without having an active data connection. Our app can be used without data bundles or with data turned off completely.

• Statement - Review, interact and action your M-PESA transactions, as well as filter, download and export your M-PESA statement in PDF form

• Receipts - Download and share e-receipts for send money, pay with M-PESA, and withdraw to share transaction information with other users via pdf

• My Spend - Allows you to track your M-PESA spend per month with aggregate and daily average spend, as well as a more detailed view with transactions broken down by category. You can change transaction's categories to fit your lifestyle

• Biometric Authentication - Log in and transact on the app using face or fingerprint authentication without having to enter M-PESA PIN manually every time

• QR - Initiate send money, pay with M-PESA and withdraw transactions by scanning QR codes. You can also generate and share your own personal QR code.

• Frequents and Favorites - Get an automatically generated list of people or businesses you frequently send money to, or save them to your favorite's list so you don’t have to manually enter their details every time you want to make a payment

• Profile picture - Take or upload your profile picture, other users will see it when transacting with you.
